BULGARIA: BULGARIA OFFERS 2.2 BLN LVS DISCOUNT T-BILLS AUG21.BULGARIA OFFERS 2.2 BLN LVS DISCOUNT T-BILLS AUG21.Bulgaria's Finance Ministry willoffer a special issue of 2.2 billion levs worth of 34-daydiscount T-bills at an auction on Wednesday, the BulgarianNational Bank (BNB) said.Settlement for the auction would be made on Thursday,August 22, at the average accepted price.Details of the issue follow: Issue number	BG 3015996005 Par value	   2.2 billion levs Auction date	August 21, 1996 Issue date	  August 22, 1996 Maturity date     September 25, 1996-- Sofia Newsroom, (++359-2) 981 8569